%N A396146 Expansion of 1/sqrt((1-x^2)*(1-2*x)).
%C A396146 Divided by n!, these are the coefficients c_n in (2.45) and (2.46) in the article by Deléglise and Nicolas, which are needed in the calculation for A395934.
%H A396146 Marc Deléglise and Jean-Louis Nicolas, <a href="https://doi.org/10.1017/S1446788718000083">An arithmetic equivalence of the Riemann hypothesis</a>, Journal of the Australian Mathematical Society, Volume 106, Issue 2, April 2019, pp. 235-273.
%o A396146 (PARI) my(x='x+O('x^22)); Vec(serlaplace(1/sqrt((1-x^2)*(1-2*x))))
%Y A396146 Cf. A395934.
%K A396146 nonn
%O A396146 0,3
